Task:

Count the occurence the word 'are' in the given file


val newfile = sc.textFile("/user/stgvenu9/json_files/wc.txt")
val a = newfile.flatMap(rec => rec.split(" "))
val b = a.map(rec => (rec,1))
val areWc = sc.accumulator(0,"'are' count")
val c = b.filter(rec => { 
if (rec._1 == "are")
(areWc += 1)
rec._1 == "are"
})
